# OmnibusDEX deploy harness — local secrets.
#
# 1. Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored).
# 2. Paste the private key for slot 6 (tornetwork.omnibus, 0xc5A63d78B451768Ba1dc799Fb08Ad41c6b37C938).
#    Derive once locally with:
#      cd ../../
#      # any tool that runs BIP-44 m/44'/60'/0'/0/6 against the founder mnemonic
# 3. chmod 600 .env
# 4. npm run deploy:sepolia
#
# The privkey NEVER leaves this file. Hardhat reads it, signs the deploy
# tx, and that's it — no broadcast of the key anywhere.

DEPLOYER_PRIVKEY=0xPASTE_SLOT_6_PRIVKEY_HEX_HERE

# Optional: override the operator address. Default is slot 2 (exchange.omnibus).
# OPERATOR_EVM_ADDRESS=0x2680Cf2201300F4eCF3fd8a592D9aA760122C3E0

# Optional: override RPC URLs. Defaults work for testnets.
# SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.drpc.org
# BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.base.org
# LIBERTY_RPC_URL=https://rpc.testnet.lcx.com

# Optional: for `hardhat verify` to publish source on Etherscan after deploy.
# ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=
# BASESCAN_API_KEY=
